external_knowledge:
- 'beacons of meteorological vigilance' refers to active weather stations; 
- 'San Francisco vicinity' is defined by latitude 37.77 to 37.80 and longitude -122.42 to -122.39; 
- 'sentinels of the skies' refers to observers.

sql:
SELECT station_name
FROM weather_stations
WHERE station_id = 'CAE010';
